          <h1>
           Decorate Your Windows With Our Choicest Valences
          </h1>
          Valences add an elegant and much-needed touch to any window treatment. They conceal the window drapery equipment such as rods or other hardware, offering a soft feel to your room. When you buy valences for your windows, you must look for the right shades and patterns to go with your curtains and the rest of your room's design. Whether the style of your room is Victorian, contemporary, romantic, traditional, ethnic, cottage or country style, you can choose the right type of valences to add oomph and flavour to the overall dcor.
          <br/>
          <br/>
          <h2>
           Valences Galore At Deco Window
          </h2>
          <br/>
          At Deco Window, you will find a variety of valence designs such as Waterfall, Trumpet, Brush, Scalloped and Ascot valances, which come in several colours, fabrics and trim styles. Before you buy valence of a particular type, make sure its colour, fabric and style matches your room's ambience. With excellent prices and great value for your money, Deco Window valences will make your room come alive. Check out our current promotions and offers, before you buy valences from our online or retail stores and get the best price for your purchase!
          <br/>
          <br/>
          <h2>
           Customise Your Valences
          </h2>
          <br/>
          Before you buy valences, review Deco Window's website for ideas and trends on the latest valence designs. The website's knowledge-base has a good how-to-guide that will help you select the right valence style, size and colour to match your window design. If you do not find the valence style you are looking for at our retail partners or on our website, feel free to write to us with the specifications that you are looking for, and we will be happy to help you find the valence of your choice.
          <br/>
          <br/>
          With decades of experience in the home and interior design industry, Deco Window leaves no stone unturned to ensure the best standards in product quality and customer service. Our products are elegant, long-lasting and absolutely worth the price you pay for them. So buy valences and other window treatment products at Deco Window today!
